<HEADLINE>
AMGEN, HARVARD FIND ALZHEIMER'S `HOLY GRAIL'
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY JASON Z. COHEN  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   THOUSAND OAKS, CALIF. -- Researchers at biotech giant Amgen Inc.
