<P>
   POTTER-ROWLING _ Profile of J.K. Rowling, Scottish author of the
wildly popular Harry Potter series of children's books, about the
adventures of a young boy at an eccentric school for wizards.
(Hulbert, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 35. WITH PHOTOS. MOVED
</P>
