   &UR; NEW YORK &LR;  (``a'' code)
</P>
<P>
   NY-KLAN-MARCH (New York) _ Developments on the planned Saturday
march by the Ku Klux Klan in Manhattan as the city appeals a court
decision permitting the march. By Benjamin Weiser.
</P>
<P>
   We are also monitoring for a possible court decision in the
city's effort to evict the Brooklyn Museum from its building
following the opening of the controversial ``Sensation'' exhibit.
