<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-22 15:19 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5188 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e BC-BOOK-DOG-BOS &LR;      10-22 0851
