<P>
   RUNNER. Ed Burnham of Kansas City has run in more than 60
marathons, and will run on Sunday in the Rib Run Marathon. Thing
is, he didn't start running them until he was 70 years old. He will
be 80 and the oldest runner entered in the marathon. Katie Funk.
20. Photo, graphic
</P>
<P>
   SIMAS. The Attack, which opens its season on Saturday, is
counting heavily on Brazilian Clovis Simas. Howard Richman. 16.
Photo.
