   &UR; OTHER SPORTS &LR;  (``s'' code)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-REPORT (Undated) _ Saturday's college football matchups. By
Frank Litsky.
</P>
<P>
   BOX-TYSON-NORRIS (Las Vegas) _ Advance on Saturday's Mike
Tyson-Orlin Norris fight. By Timothy W. Smith.
</P>
