considered overpriced and esoteric become mainstream, gotta-have-it
features. We've seen this with modems, scanners, color printers and
digital cameras. Now, the latest hot peripheral is the writable and
rewritable CD-ROM drive. By DWIGHT SILVERMAN. (Already filed.)
