hard for employers to find good workers. So where can a company
turn when it has to hire a lot of workers for a short time? Six
Flags AstroWorld has hit upon a winning formula _ it finds
charitable groups to bring in volunteers to work during the park's
Halloween promotion. By L.M. SIXEL. (Already filed.)
