   &LR;
</P>
<P>
   A graphic that moved Oct. 13 with AIDS-AFRICA-I (i), the first
story in the series, erroneously labeled Ivory Coast as Nigeria.
</P>
<P>
   AIDS-AFRICA-II (i) and an accompanying graphic described the
