98 at 2000-compliant. A bigger worry might by how your various
applications, such as word processing programs, might perform. You
might just want to run into a cave and hide. By DR. EMILIO BOMBAY.
Story has moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
