<P>
   CLINTON-WAR-POWERS (Washington) _ Does the White House or
Congress have the right to send American troops into battle? That
constitutional question is argued before a federal appeals court
here as 31 House members urge the three-judge panel to let them
challenge President Clinton's authority when he ordered the bombing
of Yugoslavia. By MARK HELM. (Already filed.)
