<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-22 22:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5730 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-BBO-KRIKORIAN-COLUMN-     10-22 1181
